<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为了弘扬雷锋精神，培养当代大学生勤俭节约，艰苦奋斗的良好品德。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red;">3月5日，经济管理学院开展学习雷锋好榜样“践行雷锋精神，美化环境卫生”活动，全体学生党员、第二十七期、第二十八期入党积极分子、劳动协会、学生会、融媒体协会、班团联合会等学生组织，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; visibility: visible;">参加了本次活动。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">践行雷锋好榜样，我们需要雷锋，我们更需要做雷锋，不只是3月5日这一天，而是生命中的每一天。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red;">培养青少年关爱他人、服务社会的优良品质，学习雷锋好榜样，经管学子在行动。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJ1icacXhYic7ryibPE55GtgS1icoMhnBtgias3x5NXJiap8ibvnnJhgAmnXCXqhXt7x1kHKvVuNVCVB2MmA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="370" height="235" style="width: 370px; height: 235px;"/></p>